OpenCL Device - GPU
Compute Unit - Streaming Multiprocessor (SM)
Processing Element - Scalar Processor (SP)

WorkingGroupId - Id of cluster of kernels
WorkItemId - Id of a kernel


Global memory - all kernels have access to it

Constant memory - reference to main device's memory or
                  constant cache of Compute Unit if there is one.

Local memory - all kernels within Compute Unite have access to it.
               also called SHARED MEMORY

Private memory - a working item registers.


